BBV could approve share split on Friday . The board of Spanish bank Banco Bilbao Vizcaya could approve on Friday the halving of the nominal value of its shares , which had been previously announced , sources at the bank said . BBV previously said it would split the shares were they to exceed 10 , 000 pesetas a share . On Thursday , BBV closed down 250 pesetas a share at 10 , 090 . - - Madrid Newsroom + 34 1 585 2167 
